_sText:
This is the final release of bhop_QuiSt, a map that I was too lazy to finish years ago.

Lots of things have changed if you have played on the beta map : 
This one is way harder, longer, more beautiful, and way more fun to play. 

If you're looking for challenge, this is the map you need. Try it, enjoy it, and write a feedback if you want to.

There's a hidden place that allows you to get above the map.


Enjoy.






Special Thanks to Dotty, RAW- and Wouit.
